INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (179,1,'2020-09-27 13:47:06','2020-09-27 03:47:06','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>VeriSkills is owned by Queensland Tertiary Admissions Centre (QTAC), a registered educational charity, whose shareholders are seven Queensland universities. QTAC has over 40 years experience verifying skills and experience for university entrance.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Who owns VeriSkills?','','publish','closed','closed','','who-owns-veriskills','','','2020-09-28 10:44:55','2020-09-28 00:44:55','',0,'https://veriskills.local/?post_type=faq&#038;p=179',10,'faq','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (180,1,'2020-09-27 13:47:06','2020-09-27 03:47:06','','Who owns VeriSkills?','','inherit','closed','closed','','179-revision-v1','','','2020-09-27 13:47:06','2020-09-27 03:47:06','',179,'https://veriskills.local/179-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (181,1,'2020-09-27 13:47:55','2020-09-27 03:47:55','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Institute for Working Futures Pty Ltd and the Queensland Tertiary Admissions Centre (QTAC) examined decades of research across multiple institutions to validate the most important capabilities for the future workplace.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The validation project isolated 14 capabilities as the most important \'soft\' or non-technical skills and knowledge required in the future workforce. While not devaluing technical knowledge and skills, these human capabilities emphasise an individuals overall employability and enable identification of high potential individuals with the talent to succeed in the workforce.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','How were the capabilities developed?','','publish','closed','closed','','how-were-the-capabilities-developed','','','2020-09-28 10:45:32','2020-09-28 00:45:32','',0,'https://veriskills.local/?post_type=faq&#038;p=181',20,'faq','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (182,1,'2020-09-27 13:47:55','2020-09-27 03:47:55','','How were the capabilities developed?','','inherit','closed','closed','','181-revision-v1','','','2020-09-27 13:47:55','2020-09-27 03:47:55','',181,'https://veriskills.local/181-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (183,1,'2020-09-27 13:48:12','2020-09-27 03:48:12','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you have received a VeriSkills credential it is a significant achievement. Take credit for your abilities and increase your chances of being noticed by your network and potential employers by displaying your badge over LinkedIn, Facebook, Twitter and other social media platforms.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Because digital credentials are issued and verified online, unlike paper certificates, they make it easy for individuals to demonstrate their competencies to employers, education providers and peers online.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','How is displaying my achievement as a badge useful?','','publish','closed','closed','','how-is-displaying-my-achievement-as-a-badge-useful','','','2020-09-28 10:45:54','2020-09-28 00:45:54','',0,'https://veriskills.local/?post_type=faq&#038;p=183',30,'faq','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (184,1,'2020-09-27 13:48:12','2020-09-27 03:48:12','','How is displaying my achievement as a badge useful?','','inherit','closed','closed','','183-revision-v1','','','2020-09-27 13:48:12','2020-09-27 03:48:12','',183,'https://veriskills.local/183-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (185,1,'2020-09-27 13:48:29','2020-09-27 03:48:29','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Yes, you can. We encourage you to strive to improve your capabilities as you progress through your career. Included in the meta data for each digital credential are suggested activities that you can undertake to improve your skills.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As you earn more credentials, you can group them in ways that are meaningful to your audience or the subject matter they have in common.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Can I upgrade my credential?','','publish','closed','closed','','can-i-upgrade-my-credential','','','2020-09-28 10:46:50','2020-09-28 00:46:50','',0,'https://veriskills.local/?post_type=faq&#038;p=185',40,'faq','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (186,1,'2020-09-27 13:48:29','2020-09-27 03:48:29','','Can I upgrade my credential?','','inherit','closed','closed','','185-revision-v1','','','2020-09-27 13:48:29','2020-09-27 03:48:29','',185,'https://veriskills.local/185-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (187,1,'2020-09-27 13:49:31','2020-09-27 03:49:31','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Getting your program assessed is a great opportunity to show that your program is consistent with industry<br>standard soft skills.<br>Additional benefits include:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Using your accreditation as a marketing tool</li><li>Internal promotion opportunities within large in organisations</li><li>An accredited course is a valuable tool for recruiting new staff who know that training they complete has currency with other organisation by ascribing external meaning to internal training</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->','Why should I get my program assessed?','','publish','closed','closed','','why-should-i-get-my-program-assessed','','','2020-09-27 18:45:22','2020-09-27 08:45:22','',0,'https://veriskills.local/?post_type=faq&#038;p=187',50,'faq','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (188,1,'2020-09-27 13:49:31','2020-09-27 03:49:31','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Getting your program assessed is a great opportunity to show that your program is consistent with industry<br>standard soft skills.<br>Additional benefits include:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Using your accreditation as a marketing tool</li><li>Internal promotion opportunities within large in organisations</li><li>An accredited course is a valuable tool for recruiting new staff who know that training they complete has currency with other organisation by ascribing external meaning to internal training</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->','Why should I get my program assessed?','','inherit','closed','closed','','187-revision-v1','','','2020-09-27 13:49:31','2020-09-27 03:49:31','',187,'https://veriskills.local/187-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (189,1,'2020-09-27 13:50:07','2020-09-27 03:50:07','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>QTAC has extensive relationships with education providers. Entry into a course is set by an in individual provider and entry requirements will vary between courses. We expect providers will use VeriSkills in assisting with entry.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Will my credentials get me access into a course of further study?','','publish','closed','closed','','will-my-credentials-get-me-access-into-a-course-of-further-study','','','2020-09-28 10:47:30','2020-09-28 00:47:30','',0,'https://veriskills.local/?post_type=faq&#038;p=189',60,'faq','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (190,1,'2020-09-27 13:49:58','2020-09-27 03:49:58','','Will my credentials get me access into a course of further study?','','inherit','closed','closed','','189-revision-v1','','','2020-09-27 13:49:58','2020-09-27 03:49:58','',189,'https://veriskills.local/189-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (191,1,'2020-09-27 13:50:23','2020-09-27 03:50:23','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The technology used on the Acclaim Platform is based on the Open Badge Standards maintained by IMS Global. This enables you to manage, share and verify your competencies digitally.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','How can I share the capabilities that I have achieved?','','publish','closed','closed','','how-can-i-share-the-capabilities-that-i-have-achieved','','','2020-09-28 10:47:45','2020-09-28 00:47:45','',0,'https://veriskills.local/?post_type=faq&#038;p=191',70,'faq','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (192,1,'2020-09-27 13:50:23','2020-09-27 03:50:23','','How can I share the capabilities that I have achieved?','','inherit','closed','closed','','191-revision-v1','','','2020-09-27 13:50:23','2020-09-27 03:50:23','',191,'https://veriskills.local/191-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (193,1,'2020-09-27 13:50:39','2020-09-27 03:50:39','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>VeriSkills will provide the details of your credential to Acclaim, who will email you with details of how to access your digital badge.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you have an existing Acclaim account, log into that. If not, you will need to create an Acclaim account at <a href=\"http://youracclaim.com\">www.youracclaim.com</a>. You can then log in and claim your badge.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','How do I access my digital badges?','','publish','closed','closed','','how-do-i-access-my-digital-badges','','','2020-09-28 10:48:07','2020-09-28 00:48:07','',0,'https://veriskills.local/?post_type=faq&#038;p=193',80,'faq','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (194,1,'2020-09-27 13:50:39','2020-09-27 03:50:39','','How do I access my digital badges?','','inherit','closed','closed','','193-revision-v1','','','2020-09-27 13:50:39','2020-09-27 03:50:39','',193,'https://veriskills.local/193-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (195,1,'2020-09-27 13:50:52','2020-09-27 03:50:52','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Using Acclaim\'s sharing options, earners can share their badges directly to LinkedIn, Twitter, and Facebook from their Acclaim account.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To share your badge:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><li>Log into your account on<a href=\"http://youracclaim.com\">www.youracclaim.com</a></li><li>Select the badge you would like to share</li><li>At the top of the page, select the blue Share button</li><li>You will be brought to the Share Badge screen where you can find different tabs directing you to connect your social media accounts and share your badge</li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Once your social media account is connected, just click Share to share your digital badge.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','How do I share my badge?','','publish','closed','closed','','how-do-i-share-my-badge','','','2020-09-28 10:49:30','2020-09-28 00:49:30','',0,'https://veriskills.local/?post_type=faq&#038;p=195',90,'faq','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (196,1,'2020-09-27 13:50:52','2020-09-27 03:50:52','','How do I share my badge?','','inherit','closed','closed','','195-revision-v1','','','2020-09-27 13:50:52','2020-09-27 03:50:52','',195,'https://veriskills.local/195-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (197,1,'2020-09-27 13:51:11','2020-09-27 03:51:11','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can easily configure your privacy settings in the Acclaim platform. You are in complete control of the information about yourself that is made public.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','What if I dont want my badge to be public?','','publish','closed','closed','','what-if-i-dont-want-my-badge-to-be-public','','','2020-09-28 10:49:45','2020-09-28 00:49:45','',0,'https://veriskills.local/?post_type=faq&#038;p=197',100,'faq','',0);
